  21,6,Not a ňĻsingleňļ society We destroyed before them ever believed ňĻafter receiving the signsňļ. Will these ňĻpagansňļ then believe
  21,7,"We did not send ňĻmessengersňļ before you ňĻO Prophetňļ except mere men inspired by Us. If you ňĻpolytheistsňļ do not know ňĻthis alreadyňļ, then ask those who have knowledge ňĻof the Scripturesňļ"
  21,8,"We did not give those messengers ňĻsupernaturalňļ bodies that did not need food, nor were they immortal"
